{"tid":2026428,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"唔講唔覺，原來香港金管局都有研究央行數碼貨幣(CBDC)","createTime":"2020-05-21T02:55:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T13:24:20.000Z","uid":351009,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b9c8ea31b1a537b183bfe77065aca77d406d1ff4","tid":2026428,"uid":351009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T02:55:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2tTGypi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2tTGypi.png&h=ed8391c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MHoy8XG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMHoy8XG.png&h=77b10cf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nHKMA 2017年開始研究Project LionRock<br />\n匯豐、中銀、渣打、香港銀行同業結算公司都有參加，已經做到發行數碼港幣同債券、貨銀對付(DVP)系統<br />\n<br />\n2019年加埋泰國央行個Project Inthanon一齊玩Inthanon-LionRock <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(Inthanon係泰國第一高山，位於清邁)<br />\n兩邊夾埋有10間銀行參加，主要研究跨境代幣兌換、實時轉帳、fx trading、liquidity management同監管<br />\n<br />\n值得一提嘅係兩邊都係用R3 Corda嘅技術，屬於permissioned blockchain，需要授權先可以加入，不過我睇其他新聞話未必出俾普通人用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實美國唔出CBDC香港用聯繫匯率有機會食下頭啖湯，尤其經濟危機下全世界對美元有需求，人民幣就算有技術優勢都唔夠美金高認受性，但HKMA敢唔敢出港幣retail CBDC似乎就係政治問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">政府新聞稿: <a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202001/22/P2020012200534.htm?fontSize=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202001%2F22%2FP2020012200534.htm%3FfontSize%3D1&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsRhXM9JohKQ1t0lxADMilzY%3D&h=368c136f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202001/22/P2020012200534.htm?fontSize=1</a><br />\nFull report: <a href=\"https://www.hkma.gov.hk/media/eng/doc/key-functions/financial-infrastructure/Report_on_Project_Inthanon-LionRock.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkma.gov.hk%2Fmedia%2Feng%2Fdoc%2Fkey-functions%2Ffinancial-infrastructure%2FReport_on_Project_Inthanon-LionRock.pdf&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsRhXM9JohKQ1t0lxADMilzY%3D&h=d3e17515\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkma.gov.hk/media/eng/doc/key-functions/financial-infrastructure/Report_on_Project_Inthanon-LionRock.pdf</a></span>"},{"pid":"fb985cace5f0a1dd170d7363e796151019907961","tid":2026428,"uid":133950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T03:09:04.000Z","msg":"貌似喺因為每個政府如果無自己既數碼貨幣 經濟上會無左自主權   之前好似有research paper研究過呢個問題"},{"pid":"07b7204c0b6aabbbb5f478eee0148735d95fe3b7","tid":2026428,"uid":159913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb985cace5f0a1dd170d7363e796151019907961","tid":2026428,"uid":133950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T03:09:04.000Z","msg":"貌似喺因為每個政府如果無自己既數碼貨幣 經濟上會無左自主權   之前好似有research paper研究過呢個問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T03:40:14.000Z","msg":"咩paper嚟? 數碼貨幣仲係好新下喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9699d5603dd993ad1faf2bf195d4f884b60f440","tid":2026428,"uid":21052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:33:02.000Z","msg":"法國巴打發d po幾高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20f3c79df8f1dff8997e9cc54826216a7395333c","tid":2026428,"uid":351009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9699d5603dd993ad1faf2bf195d4f884b60f440","tid":2026428,"uid":21052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:33:02.000Z","msg":"法國巴打發d po幾高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T11:50:48.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3db94a718526fd87ccd3fb1cd5ce263d87b7ad7","tid":2026428,"uid":351009,"l